task.summary: Revert back from Virtual threads to platform threads: Virtual threads were noticed to be expensive and affected performance greatly. Rework on windows decoration behaviour: handle minimize and maximize events differently. Fix sl4j no being able to load into memory: Add sl4j-simple to combat this as advised or noted on sl4j website.
Fix issues with database handling, issues were dependency related(SQLite Driver). Fixed by downgrading dependency version.
Adding more features and functionality(More screens too) Try adding MFXTreeView for animated navbar
